<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>As on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/as/</link><description>Recent content in As on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/as/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Kotlin ClassCastException — Type Cast Failed Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/typecast-kotlin/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/typecast-kotlin/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="classcastexception--type-cast-failed"&gt;ClassCastException — Type Cast Failed&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt; occurs when you attempt to cast an object to a type it doesn&amp;rsquo;t belong to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kotlin uses &lt;code&gt;as&lt;/code&gt; for explicit type casts. If the object isn&amp;rsquo;t of the target type, the cast fails. Kotlin&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code&gt;is&lt;/code&gt; check and safe cast &lt;code&gt;as?&lt;/code&gt; help prevent these errors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Unsafe downcast&lt;/strong&gt; — casting to incorrect subtype&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Java generic erasure&lt;/strong&gt; — runtime type information lost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wrong collection type&lt;/strong&gt; — casting collection elements&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interface implementation&lt;/strong&gt; — casting to wrong interface&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Unsafe downcast
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;open&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Animal&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Dog&lt;/span&gt; : Animal()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Cat&lt;/span&gt; : Animal()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; animal: Animal = Cat()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; dog = animal &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; Dog &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Java generic erasure
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; list: List&amp;lt;Any&amp;gt; = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;a&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;b&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;c&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; strings = list &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; List&amp;lt;String&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// May throw ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: Wrong collection type
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; mixed: List&amp;lt;Any&amp;gt; = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;two&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; first = mixed[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Interface cast
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; map = HashMap&amp;lt;String, Int&amp;gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; mutableMap = map &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; MutableMap&amp;lt;String, Int&amp;gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Works, but risky
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-safe-cast-as"&gt;Fix 1: Use safe cast &lt;code&gt;as?&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; animal: Animal = Cat()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; dog = animal &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; Dog &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; dog = animal &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? Dog
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;dog&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;?.&lt;/span&gt;bark() &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Safe, dog is null if cast fails
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-is-check"&gt;Fix 2: Use &lt;code&gt;is&lt;/code&gt; check&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; animal: Animal = Cat()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; dog = animal &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; Dog &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (animal &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; Dog) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; animal.bark()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-when-for-multiple-types"&gt;Fix 3: Use &lt;code&gt;when&lt;/code&gt; for multiple types&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; animal: Animal = Cat()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; dog = animal &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; Dog &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; (animal) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; Dog &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; animal.bark()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; Cat &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; animal.meow()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Unknown animal&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-filter-collection-elements"&gt;Fix 4: Filter collection elements&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; mixed: List&amp;lt;Any&amp;gt; = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;two&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; first = mixed[&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// ClassCastException
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; strings = mixed.filterIsInstance&amp;lt;String&amp;gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-kotlin" data-lang="kotlin"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe casting with smart cast
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;process&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: Any) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;when&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; String &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;String: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; Int &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Int: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;is&lt;/span&gt; Double &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Double: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;$value&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;-&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; println(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Unknown type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: Safe collection casting
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; data: List&amp;lt;Any&amp;gt; = listOf(&lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3.0&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; strings = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.filterIsInstance&amp;lt;String&amp;gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;val&lt;/span&gt; ints = &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;data&lt;/span&gt;.filterIsInstance&amp;lt;Int&amp;gt;()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/nullpointer-kotlin/"&gt;NullPointerException&lt;/a&gt; — null dereference&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/illegal-argument/"&gt;IllegalArgumentException&lt;/a&gt; — invalid argument&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/unsupported-operation/"&gt;UnsupportedOperationException&lt;/a&gt; — unsupported operation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Kotlin ClassCastException — Type Cast Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/class-cast/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/kotlin/class-cast/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="classcastexception--type-cast-fix"&gt;ClassCastException — Type Cast Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when you attempt to cast an object to a type that it is not an instance of. This commonly occurs with unsafe casts using the &lt;code&gt;as&lt;/code&gt; operator.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kotlin&amp;rsquo;s &lt;code&gt;as&lt;/code&gt; operator performs an unchecked cast at runtime. If the object is not an instance of the target type, the cast fails with &lt;code&gt;ClassCastException&lt;/code&gt;. This is common when working with generic types, Java interop, or heterogeneous collections.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Swift Error — Could Not Cast Value of Type</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/type-casting/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/type-casting/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="could-not-cast-value-of-type"&gt;Could Not Cast Value of Type&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs when you force-cast (&lt;code&gt;as!&lt;/code&gt;) an object to a type it doesn&amp;rsquo;t actually conform to. The runtime detects the mismatch and crashes.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Swift provides &lt;code&gt;as?&lt;/code&gt; (conditional cast) and &lt;code&gt;as!&lt;/code&gt; (forced cast) for type casting. The forced cast &lt;code&gt;as!&lt;/code&gt; will crash if the object isn&amp;rsquo;t of the target type. This commonly happens with heterogeneous collections, &lt;code&gt;Any&lt;/code&gt; typed values, and decoded JSON data.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Swift Type Cast Failed — Force Cast Crash Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/type-cast-failed/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/type-cast-failed/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="type-cast-failed--force-cast-crash"&gt;Type Cast Failed — Force Cast Crash&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A type cast failure occurs when you force-cast (&lt;code&gt;as!&lt;/code&gt;) an object to a type it doesn&amp;rsquo;t belong to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Swift uses &lt;code&gt;as!&lt;/code&gt; to force a type cast. If the object isn&amp;rsquo;t of the target type, the cast fails with a fatal error. This commonly happens with protocol existentials, JSON parsing, and Core Data objects.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common causes:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Wrong type assumption&lt;/strong&gt; — casting to incorrect type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Protocol existential&lt;/strong&gt; — casting protocol to concrete type&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;JSON parsing&lt;/strong&gt; — type mismatch in decoded data&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Core Data objects&lt;/strong&gt; — casting managed objects incorrectly&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 1: Wrong type assumption&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value: Any = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; number = value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! Int &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error: Could not cast&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 2: Protocol existential&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;protocol&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Drawable&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;draw&lt;/span&gt;() }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Circle&lt;/span&gt;: Drawable { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;func&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;draw&lt;/span&gt;() {} }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; drawable: Drawable = Circle()
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; rectangle = drawable &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! Rectangle &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 3: JSON type mismatch&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; json: [String: Any] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;count&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;five&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; count = json[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;count&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! Int &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Cause 4: Core Data cast&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; object = entityManager.find(id)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; user = object &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! UserEntity &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fatal error if wrong type&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="fix-1-use-conditional-cast"&gt;Fix 1: Use conditional cast&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value: Any = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; number = value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! Int &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; number = value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? Int {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(number)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Not an Int&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-2-use-guard-cast"&gt;Fix 2: Use guard cast&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value: Any = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; number = value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! Int &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;guard&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; number = value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? Int &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;else&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Not an Int&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;return&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-3-use-switch-for-multiple-types"&gt;Fix 3: Use switch for multiple types&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; value: Any = &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Hello&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; str = value &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! String &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Works, but fragile&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;switch&lt;/span&gt; value {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; str &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; String:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;String: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;\(&lt;/span&gt;str&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;case&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; num &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt; Int:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Int: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;\(&lt;/span&gt;num&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt;:
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Unknown type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="fix-4-validate-before-casting"&gt;Fix 4: Validate before casting&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Wrong&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dict: [String: Any] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;count&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;five&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; count = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;count&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;! Int &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Crash&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Correct&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; count = dict[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;count&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? Int {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(count)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-swift" data-lang="swift"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 1: Safe protocol casting&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;protocol&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Animal&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;var&lt;/span&gt; name: String { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;get&lt;/span&gt; } }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Dog&lt;/span&gt;: Animal { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; name: String; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;init&lt;/span&gt;(name: String) { &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;self&lt;/span&gt;.name = name } }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; animal: Animal = Dog(name: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Rex&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; dog = animal &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? Dog {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; print(dog.name) &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// &amp;#34;Rex&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Example 2: JSON parsing&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; json: [String: Any] = [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Alice&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;age&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;30&lt;/span&gt;]
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; name = json[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;name&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? String ?? &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;Unknown&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;let&lt;/span&gt; age = json[&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;age&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;] &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;as&lt;/span&gt;? Int ?? &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/nil-unwrap/"&gt;Nil Unwrap&lt;/a&gt; — force unwrapping nil&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/force-unwrap/"&gt;Force Unwrap&lt;/a&gt; — bang operator crash&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/swift/decodable-error/"&gt;Decoding Error&lt;/a&gt; — JSONDecoder failure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>